Package: ReportR
Title: Repeatable Analysis Pipeline for State Summative Assessment Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Nathan", "Dadey", email = "ndadey@nciea.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a modular, repeatable pipeline for producing annual analysis
    reports from state summative assessment data. Supports four lines of analysis
    (general trends, student groups, aggregate school/district, and anomaly detection)
    and multiple output formats (docx, html, pptx).
